snippet.description:
Watch & Enjoy Jajikaya Jajikaya Lyrical Video from the Movie Akhanda 2 Thaandavam.

God Of Masses NBK, Blockbuster Maker Boyapati Sreenu, Raam Achanta, Gopi Achanta, 14 Reels Plus, M Tejaswini N Presents #BB4 Titled Akhanda 2.

Akhanda 2 Thaandavam In Theaters 5th Dec 2025

Song Details:-

Song Name: Jajikaaya
Music: Thaman S
Lyrics: Kasarala Shyam 
Singers: Brijesh Shandilya, Shreya Ghoshal

Song Programmed & Arranged by: Thaman S
Beat & EDM Works: Beyond Sound (T)
Live percussions - Thaman S, Anandan Sivamani, The Gongura Band 
Additional Live Percussions: Krishna Kishore
Guitars & Mandolin: Subhani
Flute: Shashank 
Additional Programming: Shashank Alamuru, Osho V, Hari S R

Harmony Vocals : 
Vagdevi, Sruthi Ranjani, Adviteeya, Pranati, Sindhuja Srinivasan, Sahiti Chaganti, Pratyusha, Sruthika, Vaishnavi, Soujanya, Prakruthi, Akshaya, Nadapriya, Lakshmi Meghana, Sindhuja Tanuku, Swetha, Sunayana, Savitha, Sankeerthna, Malathi, Gayatri,Kalyani, Keerthi, Likhila

snippet.description:
Get ready to vibe, groove, and go RUM RUM RUM! 
A power-packed musical ride full of energy, attitude, and chaos  featuring Ashish Chanchlani in a never-seen-before avatar!
With electrifying vocals by Nakash Aziz, catchy lyrics by Laado Suwalka, and thumping beats composed by Sreejith Narayanan, this oneâ€™s pure madness directed by the one and only and  the legendary choreographer Bosco Leslie Martis.
Turn up the volume  the RUM has just begun!

snippet.description:

Presenting the Lyrical of ''Alohomora - The True Emperor'' from the movie ''The Devil'' starring Challenging Star Darshan, Rachana Rai and others. Shri Jaimatha Combines, in association with Saregama a Yoodlee Films, presents the much-awaited film The Devil. 

Song Credits:
Name: Alohomora - The True Emperor

Poster Design : Ashwin Ramesh (Win Designs)
PR & Marketing : Purvi Kulkarni
PRO : Sudhindra Venkatesh
Digital PR : Pavan Venkatesh

Lyrics:
Pallavi:
Alohomora The True Emperor
Doubtey Beda Saitaanu Devare..
Astalavista Helade Iro
Bandhanadale Takaraaru Tondare

Kaliyugadee Krishna Yaarole
Asali Kali Yaaru Helale ?
Huttuvudu Saavinindale
Beta Belaku Baap Hai Kattale

If There Is A Will
Youâ€™ll Find Evil
Brace Yourself And See
Whoâ€™s The Real Devil â€¦.

Cho - All Rise For The Devil â€¦.

Janana Marana Naduve Vyasana Payana
Parama Satya Onde Jagada Nidhana

Kaliyugadee Krishna Yaarole
Asali Kali Yaaru Helale ?
Huttuvudu Saavinindale
Beta Belaku Baap Hai Kattale

If There Is A Will

Brace Yourself And See
Whoâ€™s The Real Devil â€¦.

snippet.title: DHURANDHAR Trailer Reaction! | Ranveer Singh | Sanjay Dutt | Akshaye Khanna
snippet.description:
Achara, Brandon and Vivan dive into the explosive trailer of Dhurander, a powerhouse Pan-India action spectacle set to redefine mass cinema! Directed with fierce vision and packed with electrifying screen presence, Dhurander brings together an unstoppable blend of high-octane action, gripping drama, and larger-than-life storytelling.

Set against the backdrop of political power, legacy, and rebellion, Dhurander follows a fearless hero rising against corruption, injustice, and a system designed to break him. With thunderous dialogue, intense character moments, and jaw-dropping set pieces, this trailer delivers every bit of the adrenaline fans were waiting for.

       (With immense sorrow in our hearts, we bring to you Heart-throb Yatra, in association with Studio Chant Audio Vision and NK Production.
This is our humble tribute to Zubeen Garg, the voice we grew up with, the music that healed us, the artist who became our own.
More than 100 artistes and the entire musical/technical fraternity of Assam have joined hands in this special journey to honour his unforgettable contribution to our music, our culture, and our lives.)
Heart-throb Yatra is our way of saying thank you...for the songs that made us smile, for the lyrics that gave us strength and for being the heartbeat of Assam.

       (With immense sorrow in our hearts, we bring to you Heart-throb Yatra, in association with Studio Chant Audio Vision and NK Production.
This is our humble tribute to Zubeen Garg, the voice we grew up with, the music that healed us, the artist who became our own.
More than 100 artistes and the entire musical/technical fraternity of Assam have joined hands in this special journey to honour his unforgettable contribution to our music, our culture, and our lives.)
Heart-throb Yatra is our way of saying thank you...for the songs that made us smile, for the lyrics that gave us strength and for being the heartbeat of Assam.

snippet.title: Friends (4K) | Official Trailer | Vijay | Suriya | Vadivelu | Siddique
snippet.description:
A man values his best friend more than anything else in the world. One day he confesses a dark secret from their childhood to his wife, which is overheard by another. Once the secret gets out, the friendship is destroyed.

Movie Credits:

Directed by: Siddique
Written by: Siddique
Produced by: Appachan
Starring: Vijay, Suriya, Ramesh Khanna, Devayani, Vadivelu
Cinematography: Anandakuttan
Edited by: B. Lenin & V. T. Vijayan
Music by: Ilaiyaraaja
Production company: Swargachitra
4k Remasterd : Hy Studioz, Kochin
Creative Visionary Head : Boney Assanar
Coloring : Shaan Ashif
Atmos Mixing : Harinarayanan

snippet.title: Aye Meri Natkhati College Ki Ladkiyon | Yeh Dil Aashiqana | Udit Narayan | Bollywood Love Song
snippet.description:
Song Credits:
Singer(s): Udit Narayan
Music Director: Nadeem - Shravan
Lyricist: Sameer

Movie Cast & Crew:
Producer: Aruna Irani
Director: Kuku Kohli
Cast: Karan Nath, Jividha, Aruna Irani, Aditya Pancholi

Song Lyrics:

Aye Hey
La La La La La Ah Ha
La La La La La La Hey
La La La La La La La 
Laa Laa

Aye Meri Natkhati College Ki Ladkiyon Ladkiyon
Yun Mohabbbat Se Mujhko Na Dekha Karo
Meri Chaahat Meri Arzoo Ke Liye
Apni Masoomiyat Ko Na Ruswa Karo
Hai Meri Natkhati College Ki Ladkiyon Ladkiyon
Yun Mohabbbat Se Mujhko Na Dekha Karo

Jo Fisal Jaaye Main Woh Deewana Nahin
Jo Badal Jaaye Main Woh Zamana Nahin
Waar Jaayenge Khali Yeh Tere Sabhi
Teer Nazron Ka Mujh Pe Na Mara Karo
Aye Meri Natkhati College Ki Ladkiyon Ladkiyon
Yun Mohabbat Se Mujhko Na Dekha Karo

Har Kisi Ko Yeh Dildaar Milta Nahin
Itni Aasaani Se Pyaar Milta Nahin
De Raha Hoon Tumhe Mashwara Kaam Ka
Maine Socha Hai Jo Tum Bhi Socha Karo
Aye Meri Natkhati College Ki Ladkiyon Ladkiyon
Yun Mohabbat Se Mujhko Na Dekha Karo
